k, p. 368:) but Lth holds"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quw~apN","text_ar":"قُوَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be [anomalous,] originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quwyapN","text_ar":"قُويَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) I prefer the former opinion, and think it should be mentioned in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qw","text_ar":"قو"},{"kind":"text","text":", or I would rather head this art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qw","text_ar":"قو"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qwY","text_ar":"قوى"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gw","text_ar":"غو"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gwY","text_ar":"غوى"},{"kind":"text","text":". ISd holds"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quw~apN","text_ar":"قُوَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qww","text_ar":"قوو"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vuw~apN","text_ar":"ثُوَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vww","text_ar":"ثوو"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]}}